name: DigiDaigaku
intro: A collection of 2022 unique characters NFT
introduce: DigiDaigaku is a collection of 2022 unique characters developed by Limit Break, a company founded by world famous game designers Gabriel Leydon and Halbert Nakagawa. Currently, DigiDaigaku characters live in a mysterious world unknown to outsiders, but in time, details about their world will be revealed.
